  "settingsRolloverSub": "Yaushe ranar take fara",
  "hadith10": "\"Duk wanda ya ce 'SubhanAllahi wa bihamdihi' sau ɗari a rana, za a gafarta masa zunubansa ko da sun kasance kamar kumfar teku.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith12": "\"Duk wanda ya karanta Ayatul Kursi bayan kowace salla ta farilla, babu abin da zai hana shi shiga Aljanna sai mutuwa.\"\n— Nasa'i",
  "hadith13": "\"Magana mai kyau sadaka ce.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith14": "\"Duk wanda ya yi imani da Allah da Ranar Lahira, to ya faɗi alheri ko ya yi shiru.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
  "hadith15": "\"Mai kula da gwauruwa da miskini kamar mai jihadi a tafarkin Allah ne.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith16": "\"Murmushinka ga ɗan'uwanka sadaka ce.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith17": "\"Mafi alherinku shi ne wanda ya koyi Alƙur'ani kuma ya koyar.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith18": "\"Ba wanda ya ci abinci mafi kyau fiye da wanda ya samu daga aikin hannayensa.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith19": "\"Allah Mai tausayi ne, kuma Yana son tausayi a cikin komai.\"\n— Bukhari & Muslim",
