  "hadith53": "\"Kada ku raina wani alheri, ko da kuwa ganin dan uwanku da fuskar murna ne.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith54": "\"Mafi alherin ku shi ne wanda ya fi alheri ga iyalinsa.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith55": "\"Duk wanda ya karanta ayoyi biyu na ƙarshe na Suratul Baƙara a dare, sun ishe shi.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith56": "\"Duniya jin daɗi ce, mafi kyawun jin daɗinta kuwa mace ta kirki ce.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith57": "\"Addu'o'i uku ba a mayar da su ba: addu'ar mai azumi, shugaba mai adalci, da wanda aka zalunta.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith58": "\"Duk wanda ya yi mini salati sau ɗaya, Allah zai yi masa rahama sau goma.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith65": "\"Mumini madubi ne ga mumini.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith66": "\"Gaskiya tana kai ga alheri, alheri kuma yana kai ga Aljanna.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith67": "\"Ka mayar da amana ga wanda ya amince maka, kada ka ci amanar wanda ya ci amanarka.\"\n— Abu Dawud da Tirmizi",
  "hadith68": "\"Babu gajiya, cuta, baƙin ciki, takaici, rauni ko damuwa da take samu Musulmi, har ma ƙaya da ta soke shi, face Allah ya kankare wasu daga zunubansa.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith69": "\"Addu'ar Musulmi ga ɗan uwansa a bayan sa kullum ana karɓa.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith70": "\"Duk wanda ya roƙi Allah Aljanna sau uku, Aljanna tace: Ya Allah ka shigar da shi Aljanna.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith71": "\"Azumi mafi falala bayan Ramadan shi ne azumin watan Allah, Muharram.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith72": "\"Duk wanda ya yi Hajji bai yi alfasha ba bai kuma yi zunubi ba, ya koma kamar ranar da mahaifiyarsa ta haife shi.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith73": "\"Umra zuwa Umra kafara ce ga zunuban da ke tsakaninsu.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith74": "\"Ku yi gaggawa da ayyukan alheri kafin fitnoni su zo kamar yanki na dare mai duhu.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith75": "\"Raka'a biyu na Sallar Asuba sun fi alheri fiye da duniya da duk abin da ke cikinta.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith77": "\"Da kun dogara ga Allah kamar yadda ya kamata, da ya azurta ku kamar yadda yake azurtar tsuntsaye.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith78": "\"Wanda ya ziyarci mai rashin lafiya, yana cikin gonar Aljanna har ya dawo.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith79": "\"Ku yada sallama, ku ciyar da masu yunwa, ku yi sallah da dare lokacin da mutane suke barci — za ku shiga Aljanna cikin salama.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith80": "\"Wanda bai gode wa mutane ba, bai gode wa Allah ba.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith81": "\"Ba a yarda da hassada sai a wajen mutum biyu: mutumin da Allah ya ba shi dukiya ya kuma kashe ta a hanyar gaskiya, da mutumin da Allah ya ba shi hikima ya kuma yi hukunci kuma ya koyar da ita.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith82": "\"Mutum yana bin addinin abokinsa, saboda haka kowannenku ya duba wanda yake abokantaka da shi.\"\n— Abu Dawud da Tirmizi",
  "hadith85": "\"Duk wanda ya bar wani abu saboda Allah, Allah zai maye masa da wani abu mafi alheri.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith86": "\"Wanda ya rufe aibin Musulmi, Allah zai rufe aibinsa a Ranar Kiyama.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith87": "\"Ka kasance a cikin duniya kamar kai bako ne ko mai tafiya.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith88": "\"Wanda ya sawwaƙa wa wanda yake cikin wahala, Allah zai sawwaƙa masa a duniya da lahira.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith89": "\"Ladan ayyuka ya danganta ga niyyoyi.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith90": "\"Ku guji tunanin mugunta, domin tunanin mugunta shi ne magana mafi ƙarya.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith93": "\"Ku ci tare kuma ku ambaci sunan Allah, za a sa muku albarka.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith94": "\"Babu mutanen da suke zaune suna ambaton Allah face mala'iku sun kewaye su, rahama ta rufe su, sakina ta sauko a kansu, kuma Allah ya ambace su a wurin waɗanda suke wajen Sa.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith95": "\"Allah ba Ya ƙara wa bawa saboda yafewa face daraja.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith96": "\"Ka daure raƙuminka sannan ka dogara ga Allah.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith97": "\"Abin mamaki ne al'amarin mumini — komai alheri ne a gare shi.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith98": "\"Musulmi ɗan'uwan Musulmi ne: ba ya zaluntarsa, ba ya yashe shi, kuma ba ya rena shi.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith20": "\"Duk wanda ya yi azumin Ramadan da imani kuma yana neman lada, za a gafarta masa zunubansa na baya.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith22": "\"Addu'ar da ke tsakanin azana da iqama ba ta komawa ba.\"\n— Abu Dawud",
  "hadith23": "\"Duk wanda ya gina masallaci saboda Allah, Allah zai gina masa gida a Aljanna.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith24": "\"Mafi kyawun sahu ga maza su ne na gaba, mafi kyawun sahu ga mata su ne na baya.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith25": "\"Azumi garkuwa ce daga wutar Jahannama.\"\n— Nasa'i",
  "hadith26": "\"Duk wanda ya yi raka'a goma sha biyu na nafila, za a gina masa gida a Aljanna.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith27": "\"Mai gwaninta wajen karatun Alqur'ani zai kasance tare da mala'iku masu daraja.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith29": "\"Mafi kyawun sadaka ita ce ba da ruwa a sha.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith30": "\"Duk wanda ya kawar da wahala ga mumini, Allah zai kawar da wahala gare shi a Ranar Kiyama.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith32": "\"Kunya wani bangare ne na imani.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith34": "\"Duk wanda ya yi hakuri, Allah zai ba shi hakuri.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith36": "\"Ba wani daga cikinku zai yi imani na gaskiya ba sai ya so wa dan uwansa abin da yake so wa kansa.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith37": "\"Ku ciyar da masu yunwa, ku ziyarci marasa lafiya, ku kuma 'yantar da fursunoni.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith38": "\"Mai karfi ba wanda ya ci nasara a kokawa ba ne, mai karfi shi ne wanda ya mallaki kansa a lokacin fushi.\"\n— Bukhari da Muslim",
  "hadith40": "\"Ku ce 'SubhanAllah', 'Alhamdulillah', da 'Allahu Akbar' sau talatin da uku bayan kowace sallah.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith41": "\"Mafi kyawun zikiri shi ne La ilaha illallah.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith42": "\"Akwai ni'imomi biyu da mutane da yawa ke ɓata su: lafiya da hutu.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith43": "\"Ka yi amfani da biyar kafin biyar: ƙurciyarka kafin tsufa, lafiyarka kafin rashin lafiya, arzikinka kafin talauci, hutunka kafin shagala, da rayuwarka kafin mutuwa.\"\n— Hakim",
  "hadith44": "\"Duk wanda ya karanta Suratul Ikhlas sau goma, Allah zai gina masa gida a Aljanna.\"\n— Ahmad",
  "hadith45": "\"Mafi kyawun sallah bayan farilla ita ce sallar dare.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith46": "\"Sadaka tana kashe zunubi kamar yadda ruwa ke kashe wuta.\"\n— Tirmizi",
  "hadith47": "\"Mai hada zumunci ba wanda ke mayar da ziyara ba ne, sai dai wanda ke ci gaba da hadin kai ko da an yanke.\"\n— Bukhari",
  "hadith49": "\"Duk wanda ya ci abinci ya ce: 'Godiya ta tabbata ga Allah wanda ya ciyar da ni wannan kuma ya azurta ni ba tare da wani iko ko karfi daga gare ni ba,' za a gafarta masa zunubansa na baya.\"\n— Tirmizi",
